<h2>Password reset code</h2>

<p>Hello {{name}},</p>
<p>We received a request to reset your password. Use the 6-digit code below:</p>

<div class="code-block">
  <div class="label">Reset code</div>
  <div class="code">{{code}}</div>
</div>

<div class="warning-box">
  <p><strong>⚠️ Security note:</strong> this code expires in <strong>15 minutes</strong>.</p>
</div>

<p style="color: #71717a; font-size: 14px;">
  If you didn't request this, you can safely ignore this email — your account is still secure.
</p>
